ong></a>创作的主题曲“Hello You, Hello me”，以及“Kami No. 2-chan”。比如<a href="https://twitter.com/asanoruri" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Ruri</strong></a>热情地唱歌。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-300x98.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-768x251.webp 768w" width="1000" height="327" /></a></p><p>此外，在这次现场活动之前，从 6 月 7 日（星期五）起，将在 VRChat 上向公众开放一个免费的特殊世界。该设计以Victor品牌角色“Nipper”出现的图画书的世界观为基础，想象了一个坐落在被森林和湖泊包围的宁静山丘上的小镇。除了“现场会场”之外，还有展示过去的音响产品的“音乐咖啡馆”，以及耳机、收音机、移动电源等产品体验区补给品。</p><h2>演员</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-300x135.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-768x345.webp 768w" width="1000" height="449" /></a><br />・神二号 ・Omega Sisters with Honwaka Band ・浅野琉璃</p><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.u9fr5eq637yl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async"