 Hololive虚拟宇宙“Holo Earth”新区域“另类城市v1”已开放！新增 72 套服装https://www.moguravr.com/holoearth-update-2024-5/ノンジャンル人生 Tue, 14 May 2024 03:03:14 +0000 VTuberホロライブメタバースホロアース https://www.moguravr.com/?p=251018 <p>运营Hololive的Cover Co., Ltd.的虚拟宇宙项目“Holo Earth”中将开放新区域“Alternative City v1”，并于5月16日（星期四）更新Ver.0.7.0。 0.7.0 版更新 [...]</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/holoearth-update-2024-5/">帖子Hololive虚拟宇宙“Holo Earth”新区域“另类城市v1”已开放！</a>添加了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上首次出现的<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/holoearth-update-2024-5/">72 种服装</a>。</p> ; <p>运营<a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hololive</a>的<a href="https://cover-corp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.</a>的虚拟宇宙项目<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://holoearth.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Holo Earth</strong></a> <strong>”</strong>中将开放新区域<strong>“Alternative City v1”</strong> ，并于5月16日（星期四）更新Ver.0.7.0。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xiyxo9ra5113-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xiyxo9ra5113-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xiyxo9ra5113-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xiyxo9ra5113-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xiyxo9ra5113-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> Ver.0.7.0 更新将于 5 月 16 日星期四 12:00 至 18:00（JST）维护期结束后发布。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【#Holoearth】ver0.7.0 预告片【另类城市 v1】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CERR8kHweuU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-me