k" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xixg8jfq9tbs-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xixg8jfq9tbs-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xixg8jfq9tbs-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.xixg8jfq9tbs-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>位于中央大厦后面的设施“ALT BEAUTYS”是一家拥有时尚沙龙“ALT STYLE”和诊所“ALT CLINIC”的设施。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gjie7chaj373-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gjie7chaj373-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gjie7chaj373-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gjie7chaj373-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gjie7chaj373-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>在造型沙龙“ALT STYLE”中，您可以使用改变美丽点来定制您头像的脸部，包括眼睛、妆容和发型。此外，作为该设施独有的功能，您可以为每个部位（正面/侧面/背面）定制发型。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gmiue3xdw3vx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gmiue3xdw3vx-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.gmiue3xdw3vx-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/bb198055e809a59047f3a9361e5d92fe-kix.